[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0770","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0770.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0516","title":"简单网络管理协议 SNMP 社区名可猜测漏洞","description":"SNMP协议使用community name作为访问认证凭据，该漏洞源于目标设备的SNMP社区名可被推测（如使用默认值或弱密码），未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过暴力破解或字典攻击的方式猜测出有效的community name。攻击成功后，攻击者可获取网络设备或主机的系统信息、接口状态、路由表等敏感SNMP管理数据，进而为进一步渗透提供情报支持。该漏洞影响所有运行SNMP服务的网络设备、服务器及打印机等终端，CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高。建议管理员将community name修改为高强度字符串并限制SNMP服务的访问来源。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0516"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.670","remediation":"将 SNMP 设备默认的 public/private 等团体名修改为高强度随机字符串，并升级设备固件/系统至厂商修复版本（如 Cisco IOS 更新、Windows SNMP 服务补丁）。在网络层通过 ACL 或防火墙仅允许受信任的管理主机访问 UDP 161/162 端口，并优先改用 SNMPv3 启用认证与加密以彻底消除明文团体名泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0516","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-243","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-243/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/10323cb4135457b41074412d623aa2116c4e1200/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0516.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0516","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0516.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0516.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/cd275183e69131386d0c86c5a1716b6a67ff7687/references/CVE-1999-0516-2023-09-21-1730","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p65v-7qg9-x6wf/GHSA-p65v-7qg9-x6wf.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/snmp_default_communities.nasl","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest/blob/7791e876271b236b6833e2bc934b5a39586a3067/references/contrib1-CVE-1999-0516-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2014/gb_snmp_get_community.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0770.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0558","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0558.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0339","title":"Sun Solaris libauth 库缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 libauth 认证库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该库函数传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得额外的系统权限，可能提升至 root 级别。该漏洞影响多个 Solaris 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账号才能发起利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0339"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.120","remediation":"升级到已修复该漏洞的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 7 及以上），安装 Sun 官方补丁 105401-xx（针对 libauth 库缓冲区溢出）。若无法升级，限制本地用户登录并启用最小权限原则，仅授权可信用户访问系统，同时监控异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0339"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0558.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0479","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0479.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0288","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 WINS 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 WINS 服务器在处理 UDP 137 端口（NetBIOS 名称服务）的数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送大量特制的无效 UDP 帧，导致 WINS 服务进程异常终止，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP4 之前的所有版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，利用方式简单，发送随机数据包洪流即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0288"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.717","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 (SP4) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 WINS 服务对畸形 UDP 数据包的处理逻辑。如无法升级，在防火墙或主机层面阻止外部对 UDP 端口 137 (NETBIOS 名称服务) 的访问，仅允许可信内部网络通信。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://safenetworks.com/Windows/wins.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1233","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19238","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0288.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0288","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0288.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0288.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j989-83h4-x7f9/GHSA-j989-83h4-x7f9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wins_udp_flood.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0288.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0479.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0455","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0455.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0269","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.x/4.x PageServices 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.x 及 4.x 版本中存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 PageServices 查询请求，无需任何身份认证即可枚举服务器上的文件列表，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击者利用此漏洞可获取 Web 目录结构、配置文件路径等关键信息，为进一步攻击提供铺垫。该漏洞影响范围较广，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0269"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.477","remediation":"立即升级到 Netscape Enterprise Server 4.1 及以上版本，该版本已修复 PageServices 目录列表漏洞。如无法升级，在服务器配置中禁用 PageServices 功能或删除相关 CGI 脚本。鉴于 Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护，建议迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0269","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/22611","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0269.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0269.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0269","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0269.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0269.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qqpc-2hm2-rq5r/GHSA-qqpc-2hm2-rq5r.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/netscape_PageServices.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0269.json","https://github.com/idabeygunarathna/network-scanning-kali/blob/a0d5890e2fe9f211390468c6077814becf5610d6/nikto_report.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0455.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0563","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0563.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0344","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 权限提升漏洞（Sechole 本地提权）","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 存在权限提升漏洞（Sechole），源于系统对调试权限的检查不当。本地普通用户可利用该漏洞获取系统关键进程（如 lsass.exe、csrss.exe）的调试级访问权限，进而注入代码或窃取令牌，将权限提升至 SYSTEM 级别。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及早期版本，攻击者仅需本地普通用户权限即可发起利用，属于本地提权类漏洞，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0344"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-08-01","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"安装微软安全公告 MS98-009 对应补丁，将 Windows NT 4.0 升级至 Service Pack 6 或更高版本，并限制普通用户的 SeDebugPrivilege 调试权限分配。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-009","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb;en-us;Q190288"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0563.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0549","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0549.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0333","title":"HP OpenView Omniback 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"HP OpenView OmniBack 备份管理软件存在双重安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过欺骗（Spoofing）手段绕过身份验证，以 root 权限在目标系统上远程执行任意命令；本地攻击者则可通过符号链接（Symlink）攻击获得 root 权限提升。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上的 HP OpenView OmniBack 版本，CVSS v2 评分 7.5，危害等级高危，可在无需认证的条件下远程利用，导致机密性、完整性和可用性受损。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0333"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-08-01","updated":"1998-08-01","remediation":"建议升级 HP-UX 至 11.00 或更高版本并安装 HP 安全补丁 PHSS_16425（HP-UX 10.20）或 PHSS_16426（HP-UX 11.00）。若暂无法升级，可临时禁用 rpc.ttdbserverd 服务或在防火墙层面封锁 RPC 端口（111/32771 等）作为临时缓解措施，并建议尽快应用 HP 官方安全补丁 PHSS_16425/PHSS_16426 彻底修复 rpc.ttdbserverd 缓冲区溢出漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0333.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0333","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0333.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0333.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f88m-wvmg-65x9/GHSA-f88m-wvmg-65x9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0333.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82276/info.html","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/hpux_PHSS_16534.nasl","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000348.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0549.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1350","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1350.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1136","title":"HP-UX与MPE/iX Predictive组件信息泄露漏洞","description":"HP-UX 11.0及更早版本与MPE/iX 5.5及更早版本中的Predictive组件存在信息泄露漏洞（CWE-200）。攻击者可通过电子邮件或调制解调器拦截客户与Response Center Predictive系统之间的消息数据传送，导致敏感配置信息和诊断数据被未授权获取。该漏洞源于Predictive消息在传输过程中缺乏加密和认证保护机制，攻击者无需认证即可利用本地访问方式实施拦截。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1136"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1998-07-30","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"应用HP安全公告HPSBUX9807-081中提供的补丁，升级HP-UX到11.0以上版本或MPE/iX到5.5以上版本。在Predictive消息传输中启用加密和认证机制，限制对Response Center系统的网络访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://cert.ip-plus.net/bulletin-archive/msg00040.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104526177&w=2","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-081.shtml","http://www.codetalker.com/advisories/vendor/hp/hpsbux9807-081.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1413"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1350.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1318","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1318.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1070","title":"Xylogics Annex 终端服务 ping CGI 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Xylogics Annex 终端服务的 ping CGI 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的超长查询参数（query parameter）触发该漏洞，导致目标服务崩溃并引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Xylogics Annex 终端服务相关版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。目前厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1070"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:39.537","remediation":"Xylogics Annex 终端服务器（后被 Bay Networks 收购）已停产且不再受支持，建议立即将设备升级替换为仍在厂商支持周期内的终端服务器产品。若无法立即替换，可采取以下临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 Annex 管理接口和 CGI 服务（TCP 23/443 等端口）；在 Apache/Nginx 反向代理层对 ping CGI 的 query 参数长度做限制（不超过 256 字符），拦截超长请求；禁用不必要的 CGI 功能模块；监控并记录异常超长 URL 请求日志以便追溯攻击源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/10021"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1318.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1390","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1390.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1200","title":"Vintra SMTP MailServer EXPN 命令拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Vintra SMTP MailServer 在处理 EXPN 命令时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向 SMTP 端口发送特制的 \"EXPN *@\" 命令，导致邮件服务器服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Vintra SMTP MailServer 相关版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。目前厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1200"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.943","remediation":"编辑 Vintra SMTP MailServer 的 sendmail.cf 配置文件，添加配置行 `O PrivacyOptions=needmailhelo, noexpn` 以禁用 EXPN 命令，然后重启 MTA 服务。该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的邮件服务器（如 Exchange Server、Postfix）并从防火墙限制 25 端口仅允许可信 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=90222454131610&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1617","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1200.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1200","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1200.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1200.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f37077e857e7a28bab83d284c23299407fb1af7e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r4fx-3jx4-5mcm/GHSA-r4fx-3jx4-5mcm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88625/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1200.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1390.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0022","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0005","title":"Netscape Messaging Server 与 UW IMAPD 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Messaging Server 3.55 及 University of Washington imapd 10.234 的 IMAP 服务存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 IMAP 服务的 authenticate 命令发送特制超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，进而以 IMAP 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响大量使用相关 IMAP 软件的邮件服务器，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0005"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.900","remediation":"University of Washington imapd 10.234 用户应立即升级至 11.xx 及以上版本；Netscape Messaging Server 3.55 用户应升级至 4.0 或更新版本。建议在无法立即升级时，限制 IMAP 服务的源 IP 访问范围，或在不影响业务的情况下临时禁用 IMAP 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/177","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/130","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19107","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0005.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0005.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0005","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0005.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1844.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/imap.rules","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0005.md","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/uw_imap_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0022.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1362","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1362.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1149","title":"CSM Proxy 4.1 FTP 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CSM Proxy 4.1 的 FTP 代理组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 端口发送超长字符串，触发缓冲区溢出，导致代理服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞源于对用户输入长度缺乏校验，攻击者无需认证即可利用，影响 CSM Proxy 4.1 版本，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1149"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:49.540","remediation":"建议升级至 CSM Proxy 4.1 之后的安全版本（如果厂商已发布修复版本）；由于 CSM 公司及产品早已停止维护，实际可行方案为：在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 端口（21）的访问，仅允许可信来源 IP 连接；如仍需使用该代理服务，建议迁移至正在维护的替代代理产品。临时缓解措施可通过配置 Windows 防火墙或网络 ACL 阻断外部来源对 TCP 21 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525993&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1422","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1149.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1149","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1149.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1149.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rhwf-3wmm-xg4m/GHSA-rhwf-3wmm-xg4m.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88460/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1149.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000336.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1362.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1270","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1270.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1432","title":"Sun Solaris 2.6 电源管理漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.4 至 2.6 系统的电源管理（Powermanagement）模块存在安全缺陷：在系统通过 sys-suspend 挂起并恢复时，xlock 屏幕锁定进程要等到恢复操作完全结束后才启动。攻击者只需在系统恢复后的短暂窗口期内拥有物理键盘访问权限，即可在锁屏生效前向最后活动的应用程序输入字符，从而绕过屏幕锁定机制，可能以提升后的权限执行操作，进而危害系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1432"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:25.720","remediation":"升级到 Solaris 2.6 已发布的内核补丁（如 Sun 官方 105930 系列补丁簇）以修复电源管理恢复时序缺陷；若暂无法打补丁，可在系统挂起/恢复过程中物理锁定机房并禁用 sys-suspend 自动恢复功能，通过移除 /usr/openwin/bin/xlock 之外的自定义挂起脚本、改用需口令解锁的屏幕保护策略来降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525997&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/160","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19126","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1432.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1432","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1432.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1432.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-prwq-fx78-ppf8/GHSA-prwq-fx78-ppf8.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000337.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--466b019b-2c41-4010-a86d-f6bedcdb2a44.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1432.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1270.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1270.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1270.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0447","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0447.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0263","title":"Oracle Solaris SUNWadmap 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中的 SUNWadmap 管理工具包（admintool）存在本地权限提升漏洞。admintool 程序以 setuid root 权限运行，本地普通用户可利用该程序在参数处理上的缺陷，以 root 权限执行任意命令，从而获取系统完全控制权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5、2.5.1、2.6 等多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地账户，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可利用。Sun 已发布安全公告（SunSolve Bulletin #173）提供修补方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0263"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.717","remediation":"建议立即移除 /usr/sbin/adm/admap 二进制文件的 setuid 权限：`chmod u-s /usr/sbin/adm/admap`；如无需使用 Solstice AdminSuite，可直接卸载 SUNWadmap 软件包：`pkgrm SUNWadmap`；同时安装 Sun 对应补丁（如 106235-xx 系列补丁，视 Solaris 版本而定）；限制 admap 仅授权管理员可执行，防止普通用户滥用提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/173"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0447.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1461","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1461.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1297","title":"Sun OpenWindows cmdtool 和 SunOS Xview L2/AGAIN 密钥信息泄露漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.4及之前版本中的OpenWindows 3.0组件所包含的cmdtool终端模拟器及XView 3.0图形工具箱存在信息泄露漏洞。具有物理访问权限的攻击者可通过按下L2/AGAIN密钥，触发系统回显之前被隐藏的输入字符（如密码输入时的不可见字符），从而导致敏感信息被本地获取。该漏洞危害等级低，CVSS评分2.1，但利用条件要求攻击者拥有物理接触权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1297"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.333","remediation":"升级 SunOS 至 4.1.4 以上版本，安装 Sun 官方补丁 ID 100482（针对 OpenWindows 3.0）和 100483（针对 XView 3.0）。如无法升级，可在系统控制台禁用 L2/AGAIN 键绑定功能，或限制物理访问权限以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doc=fpatches%2F100452&zone_32=10045%2A%20","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7482","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1297.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1297","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1297.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1297.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wmmg-53q9-h849/GHSA-wmmg-53q9-h849.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87791/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1297.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000333.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a5f36eb9-0d57-4496-8acd-f46ac3367eda.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1461.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1271","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1271.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1433","title":"HP JetAdmin 符号链接漏洞","description":"HP JetAdmin 1.0.9 Rev. D 针对临时文件日志的符号链接保护机制存在严重缺陷。该漏洞允许本地攻击者通过精心构造的符号链接，绕过访问控制机制，直接修改目标系统上的任意文件权限。在 HP JetAdmin D.01.09 运行于 Solaris 操作系统环境中时，/tmp/jetadmin.log 文件尤其容易受到此类攻击。攻击者无需远程网络访问权限，只需本地权限即可执行权限提升操作，完成对系统关键文件的权限篡改。该漏洞影响范围限于 HP JetAdmin D.01.09 在 Solaris 系统上的部署，CVSS 评分显示该漏洞危害等级为中高危。相关厂商已发布安全补丁，建议尽快升级到最新版本以修复此安全缺陷。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1433"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:25.853","remediation":"建议将 HP JetAdmin 升级至修复该符号链接问题的后续版本（D.01.10 或更高），并联系 HP 获取官方补丁。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份删除 /tmp/jetadmin.log 并创建不可写目录或定期清理，限制普通用户对 /tmp 的写权限，或将 JetAdmin 运行账户降权至非特权用户，避免其具备修改其他文件权限的能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525988&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104526067&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/157","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19124","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1433.json","http